data.description: Beautifully updated 4 bedrm, 3 bathrm, 2 car garage home in the established Bonaire community. Located to shopping, dining, Fort Liberty & a short walk to the elementary school. Featuring a wonderful lay out. A cozy sunken den w/fireplace off the foyer that can serve as a 2nd living rm/playrm. The kitchen is open to the primary living rm w/eat in dining, white appliances & a large walk in laundry rm. There are 2 primary bedrms, 1 located upstairs w/dual vanity, stand up shower & custom walk in closet. The other is downstairs w/dual closets & an ensuite that could be used as a mother in law suite. Two additional bedrms on the 1st floor. All 3 bathrms have been updated. The back yard is newly fully fenced in w/a gardening area. The spacious 2 car garage allows for you to enter through the front & into the back yard. If you are looking for that cozy, spacious "homey" feel THIS IS IT! *new roof in 2019, NEW TRANE HVAC, upstairs HVAC recently serviced, NEW fully encapsulated crawlspace*
